This is a banana dessert. ==Ingredients== * 4 bananas * 1/4 kg ghee * 15gm cashew, almonds * 1/2 liter milk
==Procedure== #Peel the almonds. #Cut the cashews and almonds into small pieces. #Fry in ghee until golden-brown and crispy. #boil the milk until it is really thick. #Peel the bananas. #Chop them into rings and deep fry in the ghee. ::The bananas need to be good and the pieces should be cut just as many as you can fry. #Cook the bananas until they turn brown. #Mix the cooked bananas in milk and keep it to cool. #Garnish it with cashews and almonds and serve.

